{"word":"G2744 - καυχάομαι - kaucháomai - kow-khah'-om-ahee - Boast","slug":"G2744","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">καυχάομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>kaucháomai"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>kow-khah'-om-ahee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Boast"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03BA;&#x03B1;&#x03C5;&#x03C7;&#x03B1;&#x0301;&#x03BF;&#x03BC;&#x03B1;&#x03B9; - kauchaomai</b> - <i>kow-khah'-om-ahee</i><p/>From some (obsolete) base akin to that of <b>&#x03B1;&#x03C5;&#x0313;&#x03C7;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9;</b> <b>aucheo&#x0304;</b> (to <i>boast</i>) and <a href=\"#/G2172\">G2172</a>; to <i>vaunt</i> (in a good or a bad sense): - (make) boast, glory, joy, rejoice."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2620\">G2620</a>, <a href=\"#/G2745\">G2745</a>, <a href=\"#/G2746\">G2746</a>"}]}